    },
    {
      "name": "Pz IVJ",
      "size": 7,
      "loco": "tracked",
      "toughLevel": 1,
      "armourLevel": -1,
      "handlingLevel": -1,
      "speedLevel": -1,
      "desc": "The backbone of the German Panzer divisions from 1939 to 1945. She started the war as a support tank with a short gun and finished it as a front-line medium with a long 75mm that could kill a Sherman at a thousand metres.",
      "notes": "The Panzer IV was Germany's reliable medium tank — not as famous as the Tiger, not as advanced as the Panther, but available in numbers and effective across the entire war. She's the opponent your players face most often in a European theatre campaign. Heavy Armor, Tracked.",
      "weapons": [
