    {
      "name": "Pz VI Tiger II",
      "size": 8,
      "loco": "tracked",
      "toughLevel": 2,
      "handlingLevel": -1,
      "speedLevel": -1,
      "desc": "The heaviest tank fielded in significant numbers during the war. Frontal armour that no Allied gun could penetrate at combat range, and an 88mm cannon that could kill anything on the battlefield. She weighs seventy tons and breaks bridges.",
      "notes": "The King Tiger is your named threat. She outguns everything the Allies field and her frontal armour shrugs off most anti-tank weapons. Use her as a boss encounter — the players hear her coming, they plan around her, and they need a clever approach because a straight fight is suicide. Heavy Armor, Tracked.",
      "weapons": [
