    {
      "name": "BTR-70 APC",
      "size": 6,
      "loco": "wheeled",
      "toughLevel": 1,
      "armourLevel": -3,
      "handlingLevel": -1,
      "speedLevel": 1,
      "desc": "Eight wheels, an amphibious hull, and a turret-mounted heavy machine gun. She carries a squad of infantry and swims across rivers under her own power. The standard Soviet APC for decades.",
      "notes": "The BTR-70 carries infantry into combat and provides fire support with her turret-mounted weapons. She swims rivers without preparation, which changes the tactical map — obstacles that stop wheeled vehicles don't stop a BTR. Amphibious, 4WD, Heavy Armor.",
