    {
      "name": "Hover Tank (SWADE)",
      "size": 7,
      "loco": "hover",
      "toughLevel": 1,
      "armourLevel": 3,
      "speedLevel": -1,
      "desc": "A sleek killing machine that glides over terrain as though the ground were an inconvenience. The hover drive ignores rubble, rivers, and rough terrain entirely — which means your carefully prepared defensive position means nothing when one of these comes over the hill.",
      "notes": "The hover tank represents the next generation of armoured warfare. She ignores terrain, crosses water without slowing, and positions faster than any tracked vehicle. The trade-off is that hover vehicles can't dig in — she fights on the move or not at all. Heavy Armor, Hover, Night Vision.",
      "weapons": [
