      "armourLevel": -3,
      "handlingLevel": -1,
      "speedLevel": -4,
      "desc": "Four engines, a crew of ten, and thirteen machine guns covering every angle of approach. She flies in formation at twenty-five thousand feet through flak and fighters to deliver her bomb load, then flies home again. If she can. Many didn't.",
      "notes": "The Flying Fortress is your strategic bomber and your crew survival scenario. She carries ten men, she bristles with defensive guns, and she has to hold formation through flak and fighters for hours. Every mission is a survival horror session at 25,000 feet.",
