      "armourLevel": -2,
      "handlingLevel": 1,
      "desc": "The fighter that won the air war over Europe. A Merlin engine, six .50-calibre guns, and the range to escort bombers all the way to Berlin and back. The P-51 made daylight bombing possible by killing the Luftwaffe over its own airfields.",
      "notes": "The Mustang is the best all-round fighter of the war. She escorts bombers to Berlin and back, she dogfights anything the Luftwaffe sends up, and she strafes ground targets on the way home. The player character's fighter of choice.",
