      "notes": "The galley is your ancient and medieval warship. Oars give her independence from wind — she moves when and where the captain commands, which makes her the dominant naval platform from Greece to Lepanto. Her ram is as dangerous as her weapons. Heavy Armor, Oars+Sails.",
